NUMBER 3194
NAME Wasteland, tall cactus
*DESCRIPTION_START
The sand at your feet is red as fresh-spilled blood and three times as salty. It glistens with minerals and poisons that could kill the hardiest of beasts, and yet there is life. A single green cactus, as tall as any tower in Fayd, seems to touch the sky here, bursting from the sand like an arrow loosed from some cavern-dweller's sandy bow.
*DESCRIPTION_END
WASTE
DAY_LIGHT
MINEC
MONSTER_GROUP 56
IFPREVERB ATTACK -1
	ADD FLAG4 1
	IFVAR FLAG4 > 300
		RANDOM DUMMY1 1 100 0
		IFVAR DUMMY1 < 11
			EQUAL FLAG4 0
			PLREVENT 1
			CONTPLREVENT
			RANDOM DUMMY2 1 6 0
			IFVAR DUMMY2 < 3
				GENMON 74
				ECHO ALL A stone lizard crawls in.
			ENDIF
			IFVAR DUMMY2 = 3
				GENMON 72
				ECHO ALL A rockman lumbers in.
			ENDIF
			IFVAR DUMMY2 > 3
				GENMON 71
				ECHO ALL A rockman lumbers in.
			ENDIF
		ENDIF
	ENDIF
ENDIF
